---
title: Sweet Italian Sausages and Blistered Tomatoes over Cheesy Kale Polenta
description: Cheesy kale polenta has quickly become one of our favorite sides. The cornmeal porridge is all sorts of creamy and comforting on its own. But when you add in a swirl of cream cheese and shreds of fortifying Tuscan kale, it feels like a hug you can eat. We’re topping it here with sweet Italian sausages and jammy roasted tomatoes, which dribble tasty juices that make the whole meal all the more satisfying.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/w21-r13-a121b203.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/w21-r13-9749bda9.pdf
course: main course
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/w21-r13-58e6609ec6243b326f7a0ab2
time required: 30 minutes
author: HelloFresh
cuisine: North America
nutrition:
  calories: 690 kcal
  fat: 36 g
